                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
            @empty
            <tr>
                <td colspan="8" class="px-6 py-8 text-center text-gray-500">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-gray-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 13V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v7m16 0v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5m16 0h-2M4 13h2m10 0v4a1 1 0 01-1 1H9a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4m6 0V9" />
                        </svg>
                        <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏û‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏á‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏Ç‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏∏‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥</p>
                    </div>
